U.K. stocks resumed an advance,
sending the FTSE 100 Index up 0.3 percent to 6,444.78 at 3:05
p.m. in  London . The gauge earlier rose as much as 0.4 percent
and fell as much as 0.1 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
